  "stac_version": "1.1.0",
  "description": "This dataset provides annual summaries of surface water presence across the Pacific region using Landsat observations. It captures interannual variability in water extent, enabling analysis of seasonal and long-term patterns. The dataset supports flood monitoring, drought assessment, and water resource management.\n\nLineage:\nGenerated by aggregating Landsat-derived water observations into annual statistics.\n\nProcessing level:\nSummary / Statistical Product\n\nDataset type:\nAnnual time series",
